0ill%20will%20toward%20the%20US%20in%20both%20countries%20and%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20international%20trade%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20trade%20rules%20are%20valuable%20because%20they%20create%20a%20predictability%20and%20certainty%20for%20countries%20and%20for%20companies%20that%20do%20business%20in%20North%20America%20and%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Edward%20Alden%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Council%20on%20Fore%C2%AD%C2%AD%C2%ADign%20Relations.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20to%20mess%20with%20those%20rules%20for%20no%20good%20reason%20is%20truly%20irresponsible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20no%20evidence%20to%20show%20he%20is%20able%20to%20use%20tariffs%20to%20achieve%20significant%20concessions%2C%20economic%20or%20otherwise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20said%20the%20agreements%20could%20have%20been%20achieved%20without%20threatening%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsing%20the%20issues%20around%20fentanyl%20and%20illegal%20immigration%20to%20justify%20a%20trade%20war%20is%20somewhat%20bizarre%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Romel%20Mostafa%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20in%20economics%20and%20public%20policy%20at%20the%20Ivey%20Business%20School%20in%20Ontario.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20like%20we%20put%20the%20cart%20before%20the%20horse%20here%2C%20which%20is%20we%20basically%20went%20into%20this%20tariff%20imposition%20and%20counter-tariffs%20and%20then%20came%20to%20the%20discussion%20table.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlden%20said%20the%20agreements%20are%20%26quot%3Bnot%20in%20the%20slightest%26quot%3B%20a%20significant%20concession%20because%20the%20Mexican%20government%20has%20long%20had%20an%20interest%20in%20cracking%20down%20fentanyl%20smuggling%20and%20better%20controlling%20its%20border.%20As%20for%20Canada%2C%20he%20pointed%20to%20data%20from%20the%20US%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20showing%20that%20the%20northern%20neighbor%20accounts%20for%20%3Cs%3Ejust%3C%2Fs%3E%200.2%