lankers%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20make%20up%20for%20the%20damage%20Israel%20recently%20inflicted%20on%20Iran's%20air%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAli%20Shadmani%2C%20a%20senior%20commander%20in%20Iran's%20powerful%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20paramilitary%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Faerospace-defense%2Firans-revolutionary-guards-commander-says-iran-purchased-russian-made-sukhoi-35-2025-01-27%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econfirmed%20the%20Su-35%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20January%2027.%20Iranian%20state-run%20media%20have%20repeatedly%20reported%20imminent%20deliveries%20of%20these%204.5-generation%20Russian%20jets%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20which%20have%20invariably%20proven%20premature%20or%20downright%20false%20but%20there's%20reason%20to%20believe%20they're%20finally%20going%20through.%20Shadmani's%20statement%20did%20not%20reveal%20how%20many%20Su-35%20Flankers%20Tehran%20ordered%20or%20when%20it%20expects%20deliveries%20in%20what's%20seen%20as%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-iran-new-drone-may-cause-issues-ukraine-air-defenses-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIranian%20Shahed%20attack%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20Russia%20has%20used%20in%20the%20thousands%20against%20Ukraine%20since%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-air-force-could-still-have-advantages-without-russian-jets-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIran's%20aging%20air%20force%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20long%20needed%20newer%20aircraft%20and%20the%20Su-35%20brings%20significant%20capabilities%20to%20threaten%20enemy%20aircraft%20near%20Iranian%20airspace.%20But%20Arash%20Azizi%2C%20senior%20lecturer%20in%20history%20and%20political%20science%20at%20Clemson%20University%2C%20believes%20even%20an%20imminent%20delivery%20of%20Su-35s%20would%20still%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20case%20of%20too%20little%2C%20too%20late%26quot%3B