0in%20Iranian%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran's%20current%20fighter%20fleet%20is%20badly%20outdated%20compared%20to%20most%20of%20its%20neighbors%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20It%20consists%20of%20F-14A%20Tomcats%20and%20F-4%20Phantom%20IIs%20from%20the%20pre-1979%20rule%20of%20the%20last%20shah%2C%20when%20Tehran%20was%20an%20American%20ally.%20Tehran's%20only%20notable%20fighter%20acquisitions%20since%20were%20a%20fleet%20of%20MiG-29%20Fulcrums%20from%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20in%201990.%20Tehran%20also%20confiscated%20Iraqi%20aircraft%2C%20including%20French-made%20Mirage%20F1s%2C%20flown%20to%20Iran%20to%20evade%20destruction%20in%20the%201991%20Persian%20Gulf%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Iranian%20Air%20Force%20pilots%20flew%20MiG-29%20fighters%20provided%20by%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20during%20a%202023%20ceremony.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a0fafeeb4be2fff9a347ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIranian%20Air%20Force%20pilots%20flew%20MiG-29%20fighters%20provided%20by%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20during%20a%202023%20ceremony.%3Cp%3EATTA%20KENARE%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20factory-fresh%20Su-35s%20would%20be%20Iran's%20most%20significant%20fighter%20acquisition%20in%20a%20generation%2C%20they%20won't%20replace%20the%20capabilities%20of%20Iran's%20degraded%20air%20defenses.%20For%20example%2C%20Khoueiry%20noted%20they%20could%20not%20%26quot%3Bdirectly%20replace%20the%20persistence%20coverage%2C%20area%20denial%2C%20and%20wide-area%20protection%26quot%3B%20offered%20by%20ground-based%20systems%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreeces-s300-missiles-ukraine-air-defenses-at-a-critical-moment-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussian-made%20S-300%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIran%20would%20also%20need%20time%20to%20train%20crews%20and%20integrate%20the%20Su-35%20into%20its%20existing%20network%20of%20sensors%2C%20command-and-control%20nodes%2C%20and%20other%20defensive%20assets%2C%26quot%3B%20Khoueiry%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20modern%20fighters%20can%20deter%20hostile%20operations%20and%20bolster%20interception%20capabilities%2C%20they%20work%20most%20effectively%20when%20combined%20with%20robust%20surface-to-air%20defenses%2C%26quot%3B%20Khoueiry%20said.%20%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20replacing%20lost%20S-300%20systems%20remains%20crucial%20for%20any%20comprehensive%20and%20layered%20Iranian%20air%20defense%20strategy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederico%20Borsari%2C%20a%20defense%20expert%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20European%20Policy%20Analysis%2C%20believes%20the%20Su-35%20will%20significantly%20improve%20Iran's%20air%20defense%20and%20offensive%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20anticipates%20that%20Iran%20will%20try%20to%20acquire%20the%20more%20advanced%20Russian%20S-400%20to%20replace%20the%20S-300s%20it%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20it's%20not%20clear%20how%20long%20it%20might%20take%20to%20create%20a%20highly%20layered%20air%20defense%20network%2C%26quot%3B%20Borsari%20said.%20%26quot%3BLikewise%2C%20it%20will%20take%20a%20few%20years%20for%20Iran%20to%20get%20a%20fully%20operational%20squadron%20of%20Su-35s%20(time%20for%20training%2C%20infrastructure%20adaptation%2C%20integration%20of%20the%20system%20in%20the%20doctrine%20and%20concept%20of%20operations%2C%20etc).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20Israel%20retains%20an%20important%20advantage%20for%20the%20time%20being.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Su-35%20is%20a%20significant%20jolt%20for%20Iran's%20airpower.%20Borsari%20noted%20the%20aircraft's%20significant%20maneuverability%20provided%20by%20its%20Saturn%20AL-41FS%20turbofan%20engines.%20These%20engines%20give%20the%20jet%20a%20high%20climb%20rate%2C%20acceleration%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bsuperior%20kinematics%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20even%20at%20speeds%20up%20to%20Mach%202.25.%20And%20its%20Irbis-E%20radar%20can%20simultaneously%20scan%20the%20ground%20and%20air%20over%20a%20wide%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20whole%2C%20the%20capabilities%20of%20the%20Su-35%2C%20in%20particular%20the%20combination%20of%20the%20Irbis-E%20radar%20and%20beyond%20visual%20range%20R-77-1%20missiles%20with%20active%20radar%20guidance%2C%20would%20definitely%20improve%20the%20Iran%20air%20deterrent's%20combat%20air%20patrol%20capabilities%20and%20make%20it%20much%20more%20dangerous%20for%20Western%20fourth%20and%20even%204.5-generation%20aircraft%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-fighter-jets-israel-air-war-gaza-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20F-16s%20and%20F-15s%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Borsari%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20possible%20that%20Russia%20will%20also%20deliver%20the%20R-77-1%20missiles%20to%20powerfully%20arm%20the%20Su-35.%20Moscow%20similarly%20provided%20beyond-visual-range%20air-to-air%20missiles%20with%20the%20MiG-29A%20fighters%20it%20provided%20Tehran%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20remains%20%26quot%3Binferior%20from%20a%20technical%20standpoint%26quot%3B%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-strikes-iran-shows-f-35-ready-higher-level-war-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIsrael's%20stealthy%20fifth-generation%20F-35I%20jets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Borsari%20said%2C%20the%20Su-35%20could%20still%20pose%20dangers%20to%20the%20premier%20Israeli%20aircraft%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-air-force-superiority-path-iran-border-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elikely%20entered%20Iranian%20airspace%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20October%2026%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Su-35%20can%20become%20a%20threat%20by%20both%20using%20long-range%20R-77-1%20air-to-air%20missiles%20or%20by%20getting%20within%20visual%20range%20and%20employing%20its%20better%20air-superiority%20characteristics%20against%20the%20F-35.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20Israel%20will%20do%20its%20best%20to%20avoid%20%5Bwithin%20visual%20range%5D%20engagements%20and%20use%20the%20F-35%20in%20its%20comfort%20zone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20likely%20that%20future%20Israeli%20strikes%2C%20should%20they%20come%2C%20could%20use%20F-35%20stealth%20fighters%20to%20target%20Su-35s%20on%20the%20tarmac%2C%20not%20unlike%20how%20they%20struck%20air%20defenses%20in%20October.%20Israel%20may%20again%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-strike-israeli-air-force-ballistic-missiles-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20standoff%20air-launched%20ballistic%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20destroy%20these%20aircraft%20from%20a%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20Israel%20having%20demonstrated%20its%20advanced%20stealth%20capabilities%20in%20the%20past%20year%20with%20its%20effective%20attacks%20against%20the%20Iranians%2C%20there%20is%20a%20decent%20chance%20the%20Israelis%20could%20launch%20a%20preemptive%20attack%20that%20at%20least%20grounds%20a%20portion%20of%20these%20Russian-built%20fighters%20and%20prevents%20the%20Iranians%20from%20effectively%20using%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20RANE's%20Khoueiry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPaul%20Iddon%20is%20a%20freelance%20journalist%20and%20columnist%20who%20writes%20about%20Middle%20East%20developments%2C%20military%20affairs%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20history.%20His%20articles%20have%20appeared%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20publications%20focused%20on%20the%20region.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-su35-purchase-russia-air-defense-israel-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22publis