spokesperson%20for%20The%20Daily%20Beast%20said%20neither%20story%20was%20assigned.)%20A%20third%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailybeast.com%2Fjoe-biden-didnt-poop-himself-but-these-celebs-did%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elist%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20celebrities%20who%20had%20pooped%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20was%20written%20by%20an%20intern%20who%20refused%20to%20put%20her%20name%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20its%2016-year%20existence%2C%20the%20Beast%20earned%20a%20reputation%20for%20its%20scrappy%20reporting.%20The%20site%20balanced%20tabloidy%2C%20lowbrow%20scoops%20%E2%80%94%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis%20of%20Florida%20once%20ate%20pudding%20with%20his%20fingers%20%E2%80%94%20with%20more-serious%20pieces%20on%20Robert%20Mueller's%20Russia%20investigation%20or%20on%20the%20pro-life%20US%20Senate%20candidate%20Herschel%20Walker%20financing%20his%20girlfriend's%20abortion.%20(Walker%20denied%20this.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20this%20meant%20the%20Beast%20made%20any%20money.%20The%20site's%20other%20new%20co-owner%2C%20Ben%20Sherwood%2C%20told%20staff%20at%20an%20all-hands%20meeting%20in%20July%20that%20the%20outlet%20had%20been%20on%20track%20to%20lose%20%249%20million%20in%202024.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiller-trump-paulson-harris-election-wealth-billionaires-economy-taxes-policy-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBarry%20Diller%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20billionaire%20chair%20of%20the%20media%20conglomerate%20IAC%2C%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bhours%20out%26quot%3B%20from%20selling%20the%20Beast%20to%20private%20equity%2C%20Sherwood%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Diller%20hired%20Coles%2C%2062%2C%20the%20famed%20former%20editor%20in%20chief%20of%20Cosmopolitan%20magazine%2C%20and%20Sherwood%2C%2060%2C%20the%20former%20president%20of%20ABC%20News.%20The%20pair%20walked%20in%20ready%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20revamp%20a%20newsroom%20where%2C%20in%2