%2C%20the%20government%20last%20month%20allocated%20land%20for%20the%20memorial%20of%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%2C%20who%20died%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20earmarked%20a%20plot%20in%20the%20'Rashtriya%20Samiti'%20complex%20in%20the%20Rajghat%20precinct%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20former%20president's%20daughter%20said%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCalled%20on%20Hon'ble%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20ji%20to%20express%20thanks%20and%20gratitude%20from%20the%20core%20of%20my%20heart%20for%20his%20government's%20decision%20to%20create%20a%20memorial%20for%20baba.%20It's%20more%20cherished%20considering%20that%20we%20didn't%20ask%20for%20it.%20Immensely%20touched%20by%20this%20unexpected%20but%20truly%20gracious%20gesture%20by%20PM%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharmistha%20Mukherjee%20said%20in%20an%20online%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mukherjee%20had%20even%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20over%20its%20demand%20for%20Mr%20Singh's%20memorial%20and%20reminded%20them%20they%20did%20not%20even%20convene%20a%20condolence%20meeting%20for%20her%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738657200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fdf8abgq8_pranab-mukherjee-manmohan-singh_625x300_07_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanmohan-singhs-memorial-may-come-up-next-to-pranab-mukherjee-sources-7630723%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20centre%20has%20offered%20land%20to%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20family%20in%20the%20Rajghat%20complex%20to%20build%20a%20memorial%20for%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%20who%20died%20in%20December%2C%20government%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanmohan-singhs-memorial-may-come-up-next-to-pranab-mukherjee-sources-7630723%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sonu%20Nigam%20clarifies%20he%20is%20not%20on%20X%