aid%20Musk%20had%20%26quot%3Babided%20by%20all%20applicable%20federal%20laws.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20federal%20employee%20unions%20have%20accused%20the%20Treasury%20Department%20of%20giving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%20unlawful%20access%20to%20sensitive%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.dcd.277055%2Fgov.uscourts.dcd.277055.1.0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20Monday%2C%20lawyers%20acting%20for%20the%20Alliance%20for%20Retired%20Americans%2C%20the%20American%20Federation%20of%20Government%20Employees%2C%20and%20the%20Service%20Employees%20International%20Union%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscott-bessent-wall-street-treasury-secretary-donald-trump-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScott%20Bessent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Treasury%20secretary%2C%20violated%20federal%20law%20when%20he%20shared%20the%20department's%20data%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-doge-work-silicon-vallery-grind-culture-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDOGE%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20union%20groups%20are%20represented%20by%20lawyers%20from%20the%20Public%20Citizen%20Litigation%20Group%20and%20the%20State%20Democracy%20Defenders%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFederal%20laws%20protect%20sensitive%20personal%20and%20financial%20information%20from%20improper%20disclosure%20and%20misuse%2C%20including%20by%20barring%20disclosure%20to%20individuals%20who%20lack%20a%20lawful%20and%20legitimate%20need%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyers%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIn%20his%20first%20week%20as%20Treasury%20Secretary%2C%20defendant%20Bessent%20violated%20these%20restrictions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20said%20Musk%20and%20DOGE%20staffers%20had%20sought%20access%20to%20the%20Bureau%20of%20the%20Fiscal%20Service's%20records%20%26quot%3Bfor%20some%20time%26quot%3B%20but%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Brebuffed%20by%20the%20employee%20then%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20Bureau.%26quot%3B%20The%20Bureau%20of%20the%20Fiscal%20Service%20is%20a%20department%20within%20the%20Treasury%20that%20oversees%20all%20federal%20payments%20and%20collections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBessent%20then%20put%20that%20employee%20on%20leave%20and%20gave%20DOGE's%20staffers%20%26quot%3Bfull%20access%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20Bureau's%20data%20and%20computers%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20scale%20of%20the%20intrusion%20into%20individuals'%20privacy%20is%20massive%20and%20unprecedented%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20must%20share%20information%20with%20the%20federal%20government%20should%20not%20be%20forced%20to%20share%20information%20with%20Elon%20Musk%20or%20his%20'DOGE.'%20And%20federal%20law%20says%20they%20do%20not%20have%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20from%20the%20Public%20Citizen%20Litigation%20Group%20and%20State%20Democracy%20Defenders%20Fund%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20reporters%20that%20Musk%20was%20given%20access%20to%20Treasury%20data%20so%20that%20he%20could%20identify%20wasteful%20government%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20got%20access%20only%20to%20letting%20people%20go%20that%20he%20thinks%20are%20no%20good%2C%20if%20we%20agree%20with%20him.%20And%20it's%20only%20if%20we%20agree%20with%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20while%20signing%20executive%20orders%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElon%20can't%20do%20and%20won't%20do%20anything%20without%20our%20approval%2C%20and%20we%20will%20give%20him%20the%20approval%20where%20appropriate%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Monday%20that%20Musk%20was%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-special-government-employee-doge-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especial%20government%20employee%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20wouldn't%20be%20paid%20for%20his%20services.%20According%20to%20federal%20law%2C%20special%20government%20employees%20cannot%20work%20for%20more%20than%20130%20days%20in%20a%20365-day%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaroline%20Leavitt%2C%20the%20White%20House%20press%20secretary%2C%20told%20reporters%20on%20the%20same%20day%20that%20Musk%20had%20%26quot%3Babided%20by%20all%20applicable%20federal%20laws.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Treasury%20and%20Musk%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20winning%20the%20November%20election%2C%20Trump%20announced%20that%20Musk%20and%20the%20biotech%20entrepreneur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvivek-ramaswamy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVivek%20Ramaswamy%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20co-lead%20DOGE.%20Trump%20said%20in%20his%20announcement%20that%20the%20commission%20would%20cut%20wasteful%20federal%20spending%20and%20slash%20excess%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Ramaswamy%20said%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-leaving-doge-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estepping%20away%20from%20DOGE%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leaving%20Musk%20as%20its%20sole%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-elon-musk%5C%2