%20as%20well%20as%20imposing%20new%20export%20control%20on%20tungsten-related%20materials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US's%20unilateral%20imposition%20of%20tariffs%20seriously%20violates%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization%2C%26quot%3B%20China's%20Finance%20Ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20announcing%20tariffs.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20only%20unhelpful%20in%20solving%20its%20own%20problems%2C%20but%20also%20undermines%20the%20normal%20economic%20and%20trade%20cooperation%20between%20China%20and%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Xi%20Jinping's%20response%20appeared%20carefully%20targeted%20to%20avoid%20major%20blowback%20on%20China's%20economy%20while%20showing%20Trump%20an%20ability%20to%20inflict%20damage%20on%20a%20range%20of%20fronts%2C%20including%20by%20disrupting%20the%20critical%20minerals%20supply%20chain%20and%20hurting%20US%20companies%20with%20major%20operations%20on%20the%20mainland.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20restraint%2C%20coupled%20with%20speculation%20that%20Xi%20may%20do%20more%20to%20bolster%20China's%20economy%2C%20led%20to%20a%20relatively%20muted%20reaction%20in%20markets%20-%20particularly%20as%20Trump%20signaled%20a%20desire%20to%20speak%20with%20the%20Chinese%20leader%20before%20the%20tariffs%20took%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dollar%20rebounded%20after%20the%20news%2C%20while%20the%20offshore%20yuan%20extending%20its%20loss%20to%200.3%25%20and%20the%20currencies%20of%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20which%20have%20strong%20trade%20links%20to%20China%2C%20slid%20almost%201%25.%20Other%20Asian%20currencies%20like%20the%20Thai%20baht%20and%20the%20Indonesian%20rupiah%20pared%20their%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Measured%20and%20Appropriate'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20response%20was%20%26quot%3Bmeasured%20and%20appropriate%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Dylan%20Loh%2C%20assistant%20professor%20of%20politics%20at%20Nanyang%20Technological%20University%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20allows%20Beijing%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20doing%20something%2C%20without%20exactly%20reacting%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20would%20be%20seen%20as%20inviting%20further%20retaliation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20Beijing%20also%20sees%20what%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20did%2C%20and%20know%20that%20they%20can%20still%20come%20to%20some%20sort%20of%20understanding.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXi's%20government%20swung%20back%20with%20its%20retaliation%20almost%20immediately%20after%20US%20tariffs%20came%20into%20force.%20That%20action%20dashed%20hopes%20that%20Beijing%20would%20reach%20a%20deal%20to%20avoid%20the%20tariffs%2C%20after%20Trump%20said%20he%20would%20speak%20to%20Xi%20soon.%20The%20Republican%20hours%20earlier%20granted%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20a%20last-minute%20reprieve%20from%20a%2025%25%20tariff%20following%20leader%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20supplied%20about%206%25%20of%20China's%20LNG%20imports%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20ship-tracking%20data.%20China%20imports%20little%20coal%20from%20the%20US.%20Google's%20search%20and%20internet%20services%20for%20consumers%20have%20been%20unavailable%20in%20China%20since%202010%2C%20although%20the%20company%20retains%20operations%20in%20the%20country%2C%20primarily%20around%20its%20advertising%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20can%20be%20interpreted%20as%20a%20warning%20shot%20to%20US%20enterprises%20with%20a%20high-dependency%20on%20China's%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lynn%20Song%2C%20chief%20economist%20for%20Greater%20China%20at%20ING%20Bank%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20still%20hope%20that%20tariffs%20could%20get%20quickly%20unwound%20or%20pushed%20back%20after%20face-to-face%20talks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESong%20called%20the%20steps%20a%20%26quot%3Bfairly%20muted%20retaliation%2C%26quot%3B%20noting%20that%20energy%20accounts%20for%20a%20small%20share%20of%20China's%20imports%20from%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20the%20largest%20producing%20country%20of%20tungsten%2C%20accounting%20for%20about%2080%25%20of%20the%20global%20production.%20Tungsten%2C%20known%20for%20its%20remarkable%20density%20and%20high%20melting%20point%2C%20acts%20as%20a%20buffer%20against%20intense%20temperatures%20and%20is%20most%20commonly%20used%20in%20armor-piercing%20missiles%20in%20the%20defense%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPVH%20is%20also%20the%20parent%20of%20Tommy%20Hilfiger%20and%20has%20been%20under%20Chinese%20regulatory%20investment%20since%20September%20for%20allegedly%20boycotting%20cotton%20from%20the%20Xinjiang%20region%2C%20through%20the%20statement%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20issue.%20Illumina%20is%20the%20leading%20global%20provider%20of%20genetic%20sequencing%2C%20and%20a%20rival%20to%20Chinese%20biotech%20giant%20BGI%20Genomics%20Co.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20over%20the%20weekend%20ordered%20a%20blanket%20levy%20on%20Chinese%20exports%20to%20take%20effect%20after%20midnight%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20the%20US%2C%20for%20what%20he%20calls%20Beijing's%20failure%20to%20prevent%20the%20flow%20of%20illegal%20drugs.%20The%20orders%20included%20retaliation%20clauses%20that%20would%20increase%20tariffs%20if%20the%20countries%20responds%20in%20kind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20more%20aggressive%20response%20from%20Beijing%20would%20risk%20a%20spiraling%20of%20US-China%20relations%20that%20had%20been%20on%20a%20more%20stable%20footing%20since%20Xi%20and%20then%20US%20leader%20Joe%20Biden%20sat%20down%20in%20San%20Francisco%20in%20November%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20countries%20have%20resumed%20high-level%20exchanges%20despite%20persisting%20tensions%20over%20tech%20access%20and%20territorial%20disputes.%20Xi%20and%20Trump%20spoke%20by%20phone%20before%20his%20inauguration%20to%20discuss%20trade%2C%20TikTok%20and%20fentanyl.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20Monday%20the%20two%20leaders%20would%20speak%20again%2C%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20over%20the%20next%2024%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20assertion%20to%20which%20Beijing%20hasn't%20publicly%20responded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738653540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-06%2Fvhqfpq0o_donald-trump-xi-jinping-reuters_625x300_29_June_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-to-impose-15-tariff-on-imports-of-coal-lng-from-us-after-trumps-move-7629767%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20slapped%20tariffs%20on%20a%20range%20of%20US%20products%20and%20announced%20a%20probe%20into%20Google%20moments%20after%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20imposed%20a%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20goods%20from%20Beijing%2C%20reigniting%20a%20trade%20war%20between%20the%20world's%20largest%20economies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-to-impose-15-tariff-on-imports-of-coal-lng-from-us-after-trumps-move-7629767%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RGV%3A%20Made%20Rangeela%20only%20to%20capture%20Urmila's%20beauty%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738653143000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117906618%2Cimgsize-45088.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-ram-gopal-varma-said-he-was-mesmerised-by-urmila-matondkar-made-rangeela-only-to-capture-her-beauty-i-couldnt-accept-her-%2Farticleshow%2F117906544.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117906544.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERam%20Gopal%20