%3EDennis%20Beggs%20hated%20his%20first%20run.%20He%20was%2055%20years%20old%20and%20had%20been%20walking%20a%20lot%20to%20clear%20his%20mind%20while%20caring%20for%20his%20mom%2C%20who%20had%20Alzheimer's%20disease.%20He%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fhow-to-start-running%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estart%20running%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20to%20%26quot%3Bwaste%20less%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20so%20ran%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20mile%20in%20spring%202017%20%E2%80%94%20and%20thought%20he'd%20never%20do%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20next%20week%2C%20Beggs%2C%20a%20farm%20owner%20from%20Wisconsin%2C%20decided%20to%20try%20again%20and%20began%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frunning-tips-beginners-run-streak-fitness-advice-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20incrementally%20longer%20distances%3C%2Fa%3E%20each%20day.%20He%20didn't%20know%20exactly%20how%20far%20or%20long%20he%20was%20running%20because%20he%20never%20took%20a%20watch%20or%20a%20phone.%20So%20when%20his%20neighbor%20invited%20him%20to%20join%20a%2010k%20race%20on%20Independence%20Day%2C%20he%20was%20surprised%20to%20come%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222134%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dennis%20Beggs%20and%20his%20mother.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a0e94abfebcc4d029d87e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221601%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBeggs%20started%20running%20to%20clear%20his%20head%20while%20caring%20for%20his%20mother.%3Cp%3EDennis%20Beggs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20race%2C%20a%20man%20encouraged%20him%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-ran-my-first-marathon-advice-mistakes-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erun%20his%20first%20marathon%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Looking%20back%2C%20his%20first%20marathon%20in%20October%202017%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisaster%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20motivated%20him%20to%20keep%20dedicating%20time%20to%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20at%2063%2C%20he%20has%20completed%20many%20running%20challenges%2C%20including%2010%20marathons%20in%2010%20weeks.%20And%20on%20January%2031%2C%20he%20started%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F61-year-old-marathon-runner-fitness-tips-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Marathon%20Challenge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20involves%20running%20seven%20marathons%20on%20seven%20continents%20in%20seven%20days%2C%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgivebutter.com%2Fdennisbeggs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraise%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20Alzheimer's%20Foundation%20of%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeggs%20shared%20how%20he%20got%20so%20fit%20at%2063%20with%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b7087221-20da-48f4-8776-3301f1bed5ab%5C%22%3EBeggs%20started%20with%20short%20runs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20start%20out%20small%2C%20and%20then%20you%20work%20your%20way%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Beggs%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20out%20walking%2C%20and%20when%20he%20started%20running%2C%20he%20slowly%20increased%20the%20length%20of%20his%20runs.%20He%20was%20already%20fit%20from%20managing%20a%20farm%2C%20so%20he%20quite%20quickly%20was%20able%20to%20run%20for%20longer%20periods%20of%20time%2C%20while%20setting%20achievable%20milestones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESohee%20Lee%2C%20a%20personal%20trainer%2C%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-stay-motivated-to-keep-working-out-exercising-trainer-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeasing%20into%20working%20out%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20doing%20sessions%20a%20few%20times%20a%20week%20and%20not%20pushing%20yourself%20too%20hard%20is%20the%20most%20sustainable%20approach.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22