n%3Cp%3EMr%20Johnson%20criticised%20how%20deeply%20normalised%20air%20pollution%20has%20become%20in%20India.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20would%20be%20outside%20running.%20Babies%20and%20small%20children%20exposed%20from%20birth.%20No%20one%20wore%20a%20mask%2C%20which%20can%20significantly%20decrease%20exposure.%20It%20was%20so%20confusing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20questioned%20why%20India's%20leadership%20had%20not%20declared%20air%20pollution%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20emergency%26quot%3B%20and%20cited%20studies%20on%20air%20pollution's%20health%20effects.%20%26quot%3BThe%20evidence%20shows%20that%20India%20would%20improve%20the%20health%20of%20its%20population%20more%20by%20cleaning%20up%20air%20quality%20than%20by%20curing%20all%20cancers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3EOver%20To%20America%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20a%20comparison%2C%20he%20said%20that%20while%20pollution%20was%20India's%20silent%20crisis%2C%20obesity%20was%20America's.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20returned%20to%20the%20US%2C%20my%20eyes%20were%20fresh%20to%20see%20what%20is%20normalised%20to%20me.%20I%20saw%20obesity%20everywhere.%2042.4%20per%20cent%20of%20Americans%20are%20obese%2C%20and%20because%20I%20was%20around%20it%20all%20the%20time%2C%20I%20had%20been%20mostly%20oblivious%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWhen%20in%20India%2C%20I%20did%20end%20this%20podcast%20early%20due%20to%20the%20bad%20air%20quality.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnikhilkamathcio%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40nikhilkamathcio%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20gracious%20host%20and%20we%20were%20having%20a%20great%20time.%20The%20problem%20was%20that%20the%20room%20we%20were%20in%20circulated%20outside%20air%20which%20made%20the%20air%20purifier%20I'd%20brought%20with%20me%20ineffective.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnInside%2C%E2%80%A6%