22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flittle-shankus-biryani-wish-for-anganwadi-meal-kerala-ministers-reply-7629683%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Trump%20Hates%20'Tariff%20Walls'.%20Why%20Is%20He%20Building%20One%20For%20America%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20continues%20his%20internal%20and%20external%20political%20warfare.%20His%20internal%20cleaning-up%20operations%20and%20external%20muscle-flexing%20have%20consequences%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20including%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeporting%20Illegal%20migrants%20is%20on%20top%20of%20Trump's%20agenda.%20The%20number%20of%20Indian%20illegal%20migrants%20is%20significant.%20India%20has%20already%20stated%20that%20after%20verification%2C%20these%20undocumented%20migrants%20will%20be%20taken%20back.%20Trump%20has%20been%20most%20impatient%20about%20the%20expulsion%20of%20Latin%20American%20illegal%20migrants.%20He%20has%20strong-armed%20Colombia%20to%20forthwith%20accept%20deportation%20by%20US%20military%20planes%20under%20threat%20of%20imposing%20tariffs%2C%20a%20blanket%20ban%20on%20visas%2C%20etc.%20While%20buckling%20under%20Trump's%20ultimatum%2C%20the%20Colombian%20president%20has%20responded%20with%20an%20emotionally%20indignant%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Complicates%20Things%20For%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India's%20case%2C%20these%20dramatics%20are%20absent%2C%20but%20the%20issue%20was%20raised%20by%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20with%20India's%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%2C%20S.%20Jaishankar%2C%20when%20the%20two%20met%20on%20January%202.%20Trump%2C%20too%2C%20has%20weighed%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20had%20discussed%20the%20issue%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20their%20phone%20call.%20He%20said%20that%20India%20%26quot%3Bwill%20do%20what's%20right%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20taking%20back%20Indian%20immigrants%20who%20came%20to%20the%20US%20illegally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20illegal%20migrants%20from%20India%20in%20the%20US%20are%20the%20fourth-largest%20in%20number%20complicates%20the%20atmospherics%20around%20the%20issue%20of%20legal%20migration%20from%20India%20under%20the%20H-1B%20programme%2C%20of%20which%20India%20is%20the%20biggest%20beneficiary.%20The%20programme%20is%20now%20under%20scrutiny%20and%20there%20may%20be%20some%20tightening%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20reforming%20the%20scheme.%20Other%20than%20this%2C%20the%20PR%20aspect%20of%20illegal%20migrants%20flown%20back%20to%20India%20in%20droves%20will%20be%20problematic%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20as%20the%20opposition%20will%20project%20it%20as%20a%20foreign%20policy%20failure%2C%20which%20it%20is%20not%2C%20by%20any%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpillover%20In%20Europe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIllegal%20migration%20has%20become%20an%20increasingly%20sensitive%20issue%20in%20Europe%20in%20view%20of%20rising%20incidents%20of%20terrorism%2C%20law%20and%20order%20issues%2C%20lack%20of%20assimilation%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20Right-wing%2C%20nationalist%20parties%20gaining%20political%20strength%20in%20European%20countries%2C%20much%20to%20the%20dismay%20of%20Left-leaning%20and%20centrist%20liberal%20forces.%20The%20robust%20way%20Trump%20is%20dealing%20with%20the%20issue%20is%20already%20fuelling%20demands%20for%20stronger%20action%20against%20illegal%20migrants%20in%20Europe.%20Marine%20Le%20Pen%20of%20the%20right-wing%20French%20party%20RN%20is%20already%20calling%20for%20emulating%20Trump%20by%20deporting%20illegal%20Algerian%20migrants.%20Europe%2C%20however%2C%20lacks%20the%20muscle%20power%20required%20for%20this%2C%20the%20kind%20Trump%20can%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20that%20India%2C%20too%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20introduce%20an%20%E2%80%9CImmigration%20and%20Foreigners%20Bill%E2%80%9D%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20illegal%20immigration%20into%20the%20country%2C%20have%20appeared%2C%20though%20the%20dimensions%20of%20this%20problem%20in%20India%20and%20the%20legal%20and%20administrative%20means%20at%20our%20disposal%20impede%20robust%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20determination%20to%20roll%20back%20the%20%E2%80%98woke'%20agenda%20in%20the%20US%2C%20with%20all%20its%20excesses%2C%20especially%20gender%20identity%2C%20fluidity%20and%20surgery%20issues%2C%20as%20well%20as%20DEI%20(Diversity.%20Equity%20and%20Inclusion)%20programmes%2C%20will%20have%20an%20international%20impact%2C%20including%20in%20India%2C%20where%20these%20agendas%20have%20begun%20to%20take%20root%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20impact%20on%20our%20society%20of%20Western%2C%20liberal-Left%20socio-economic%20currents.%20In%20Europe%2C%20gender%20issues%20have%20become%20deeply%20embedded%20in%20political%20and%20social%20discourse%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20these%20issues%20will%20divide%20Trump's%20America%20and%20the%20EU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeaponising%20Dollar%20And%20Duties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20US's%20weaponising%20of%20the%20dollar%2C%20Trump%20is%20unabashed%20in%20adding%20the%20weaponisation%20of%20tariffs%20as%20well%20to%20achieve%20the%20country's%20economic%20goals.%20He%20had%20threatened%20to%20impose%2060%25%20tariffs%20on%20China's%20exports%20to%20the%20US%20but%20has%20not%20done%20that%20so%20far.%20Following%20his%20earlier%20threats%2C%20he%20has%20now%20announced%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20Canadian%20and%20Mexican%20exports%20beginning%20February%201%2C%20and%2010%25%20on%20Chinese%20exports.%20He%20has%20not%20yet%20imposed%2010%25%20tariffs%20on%20exports%20of%20all%20other%20countries%2C%20as%20he%20had%20threatened%20to%20do%20during%20his%20election%20campaign.%20The%20US%20Treasury%20Secretary%2C%20Scott%20Bissent%2C%20has%20recommended%20across-the-board%202.5%25%20tariffs%20on%20all%20imports%20into%20the%20US%2C%20but%20Trump%20wants%20a%20higher%20figure.%20He%20believes%20that%20these%20tariffs%20can%20raise%20enormous%20revenues%20for%20the%20US%2C%20and%20to%20collect%20and%20manage%20them%2C%20he%20is%20proposing%20an%20External%20Revenue%20Service.%20He%20is%20unbothered%20that%20unilaterally%20raising%20US%20tariffs%20would%20violate%20bilateral%20FTAs%20and%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20WTO%2C%20or%20that%20other%20countries%20would%20retaliate%20and%20trade%20wars%20could%20be%20unleashed%2C%20to%20the%20detriment%20of%20all.%20Canada%20has%20already%20announced%20retaliatory%20tariffs%2C%20and%20Mexico%2C%20too%2C%20intends%20to%20do%20so.%20Trump%20has%20threatened%20higher%20tariffs%20on%20the%20EU%20and%20the%20UK%20too.%20Europe%20will%20certainly%20strike%20back%20with%20tariffs%20on%20US%20exports%20to%20the%20EU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20also%20threatened%20BRICS%20with%20100%25%20tariffs%20if%20it%20develops%20a%20common%20currency%20of%20its%20own%20or%20takes%20any%20steps%20to%20move%20away%20from%20the%20US%20dollar.%20BRICS%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20develop%20a%20common%20currency.%20India%20has%20publicly%20disowned%20any%20such%20move.%20Russia%20has%20reiterated%20that%20a%20common%20currency%20is%20not%20on%20the%20BRICS%20agenda.%20However%2C%20trade%20in%20national%20currencies%20between%20member%20states%20is%20being%20promoted%2C%20and%20this%20dilutes%20the%20dependence%20on%20the%20dollar%20for%20intra-BRICS%20trading.%20Trump's%20threats%20are%20unconscionable%20and%20will%20only%20reinforce%20resistance%20to%20his%20bullying%20tactics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Hypocritical%20Stance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20repeatedly%20charged%20India%20with%20maintaining%20high%20tariff%20walls.%20The%20White%20House%20read-out%20of%20his%20telephonic%20conversation%20with%20Modi%20says%20that%20the%20President%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20India%20moving%20%E2%80%9Ctowards%20a%20fair%20bilateral%20trading%20relationship%E2%80%9D.%20The%20nuance%20here%20is%20important%2C%20as%20the%20language%20is%20not%20peremptory.%20A%20process%20is%20being%20envisaged%2C%20which%20would%20imply%20bilateral%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20Trump's%20position%20is%20contradictory%2C%20besides%20being%20overbearing.%20He%20wants%20the%20US%20to%20protect%20its%20economy%20and%20recover%20the%20country's%20economic%20strength%20through%20tariffs.%20He%20harks%20back%20to%20a%20time%20when%20the%20US%20built%20its%20industrial%20and%20trade%20sinews%20behind%20high%20tariff%20walls%20in%20the%201920s%20and%201930s.%20Yet%2C%20he%20would%20deny%20the%20same%20option%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20The%20India-US%20Equation%20Can't%20Be%20Fair%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20there%20cannot%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfair%E2%80%9D%20trading%20equation%20between%20India%2C%20a%20developing%20country%20with%20a%20%244%20trillion%20economy%20and%20a%20per%20capita%20income%20of%20%242%2C700%2C%20and%20the%20US%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20economy%20at%20%2430%20trillion%2C%20with%20a%20per%20capita%20income%20of%20%2482%2C000.%20The%20US%20also%20enjoys%20a%20massive%20%E2%80%9Cunfair%E2%80%9D%20advantage%20in%20the%20global%20economic%20framework%20with%20its%20control%20over%20the%20global%20dollar-based%20financial%20system%20because%20of%20the%20status%20of%20the%20dollar%20as%20the%20world's%20reserve%20currency%2C%20and%20the%20global%20fall-out%20of%20its%20fiscal%20and%20monetary%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20of%20India%20has%20already%2C%20reportedly%2C%20begun%20inter-ministerial%20consultations%20on%20addressing%20the%20tariff%20structure%20issue%20with%20the%20impending%20discussions%20with%20the%20US%20in%20view%2C%20and%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20to%20prepare%20a%20brief%20for%20Modi%20for%20his%20projected%20visit%20to%20the%20White%20House%20in%20February.%20The%20new%20budget%20has%20already%20reduced%20tariffs%20on%20a%20few%20items%20that%20would%20benefit%20US%20exporters.%20His%20US%20visit%20will%20no%20doubt%20be%20used%20by%20Modi%20to%20offer%20constructive%20perspectives%20on%20issues%20of%20concern%20to%20Trump%20while%20committing%20both%20sides%20to%20a%20stronger%20understanding%20on%20issues%20of%20shared%20interests%20and%20strategic%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EExpansion%20Politics%20Of%20Yore%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20seeks%20to%20expand%20US%20territory%2C%20to%20which%20he%20alluded%20in%20his%20inaugural%20speech.%20This%20unvarnished%20power%20politics%20of%20the%20kind%20practised%20in%20colonial%20times%20and%20in%20the%20pre-World%20War%20II%20period%20should%20be%20a%20cause%20of%20worry%2C%20as%20this%20violates%20the%20UN%20Charter%20and%20exposes%20weaker%20countries%20to%20attacks%20on%20their%20sovereignty%20by%20stronger%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20claim%20on%20Greenland%20is%20being%20presented%20by%20him%20as%20intended%20to%20%E2%80%9Cprotect%20the%20free%20world%E2%80%9D%20suggests%20that%20is%20an%20anti-Russian%20and%20anti-Chinese%20move.%20Trump's%20coercive%20telephonic%20conversation%20with%20the%20Danish%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20a%20subsequent%20affirmation%20that%20Greenland%20will%20inevitably%20become%20part%20of%20the%20US%20have%20raised%20hackles%20in%20Europe%2C%20with%20countries%20like%20France%20ready%20to%20send%20troops%20to%20Greenland%20along%20with%20other%20European%20countries%20to%20deter%20Trump%2C%20though%20Brussels%20has%20been%20timid%20and%20evasive%20in%20its%20reaction.%20The%20geopolitical%20weakness%20and%20disarray%20of%20Europe%20lie%20exposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFuelling%20Russian%20And%20Chinese%20Ambitions%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20territorial%20irredentism%20of%20sorts%20would%20serve%20to%20legitimise%20Russia's%20annexation%20of%20provinces%20of%20eastern%20Ukraine%20and%20give%20reason%20to%20China's%20expansionism%20in%20the%20South%20and%20East%20China%20Seas%20and%2C%20even%20more%20pertinently%2C%20its%20claim%20on%20Taiwan.%20It%20can%20be%20helpful%20to%20India%20in%20asserting%20its%20territorial%20claim%20on%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%2C%20but%20it%20also%20helps%20China%20in%20making%20its%20claims%20on%20Indian%20territory.%20Many%20territorial%20disputes%20exist%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20Trump's%20territorial%20expansionism%20can%20have%20exacerbating%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fall-out%20from%20US-Europe%20tensions%20would%20be%20Europe%20being%20pushed%20to%20forge%20stronger%20political%2C%20economic%20and%20technological%20partnerships%20with%20rising%20powers%20like%20India%20as%20a%20balancing%20option.%20China%20is%20an%20option%2C%20too%2C%20but%20it%20is%20also%20seen%20as%20a%20systemic%20threat%2C%20which%20India%20is%20not.%20Hence%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20European%20Commission%20President%20Ursula%20van%20der%20Leyen%2C%20that%20she%20will%20visit%20India%20for%20her%20first%20trip%20abroad%20in%20her%20new%20term%20in%20order%20to%20upgrade%2C%20along%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20strategic%20partnership%20with%20the%20largest%20country%20and%20democracy%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Kanwal%20Sibal%20was%20Foreign%20Secretary%20and%20Ambassador%20to%20Turkey%2C%20Egypt%2C%20France%20and%20Russia%2C%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Of%20Mission%20in%20Washington.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738647720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F0gu37jpo_trump_625x300_12_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ftrump-hates-tariff-walls-why-is-he