ndiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjust-wanted-people-to-laugh-fitness-influencer-performs-risky-push-up-stunt-near-airplanes-jet-engine%2Farticleshow%2F117902108.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjust-wanted-people-to-laugh-fitness-influencer-performs-risky-push-up-stunt-near-airplanes-jet-engine%2Famp_articleshow%2F117902108.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjust-wanted-people-to-laugh-fitness-influencer-performs-risky-push-up-stunt-near-airplanes-jet-engine%2Famp_articleshow%2F117902108.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDTV%20Explainer%3A%20How%20Trump's%20Decision%20To%20Shut%20USAID%20May%20Hit%20Projects%20In%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20administration's%20decision%20to%20freeze%20the%20funds%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development%20(USAID)%20is%20likely%20to%20have%20implications%20on%20healthcare%20and%20other%20projects%20and%20partnerships%20with%20India.%20Last%20month%2C%20Trump%20issued%20an%20executive%20order%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2025%2F01%2Freevaluating-and-realigning-united-states-foreign-aid%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereevaluate%20and%20realign%20US%20foreign%20aid%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20policy%20of%20the%20new%20administration%20and%20put%20a%2090-day%20pause%20on%20foreign%20aid.%20USAID%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20order%2C%20has%20issued%20a%20directive%20asking%20all%20organisations%20implementing%20projects%20with%20its%20support%20in%20India%20to%20suspend%20work%20until%20further%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20chief%20and%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20Trump%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20on%20Monday%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWith%20regards%20to%20the%20USAID%20stuff%2C%20I%20went%20over%20it%20with%20(the%20president)%20in%20detail%20and%20he%20agreed%20that%20we%20should%20shut%20it%20down.%26quot%3B%20Musk%20believes%20USAID%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bcriminal%20organisation%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Btime%20for%20it%20to%20die%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUSAID%20is%20a%20criminal%20organization.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTime%20for%20it%20to%20die.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FsWYy6fyt1k%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FsWYy6fyt1k%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1886102414194835755%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%202%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20media%20briefing%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20USAID%2C%20Trump%20called%20the%20organization%20%26quot%3Ba%20group%20of%20radical%20left%20lunatics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20the%20concept%2C%20but%20they%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20radical%20left%20lunatics.%20The%20concept%20of%20it%20is%20good%20but%20it's%20all%20about%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUSAID%20Funding%20In%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSAID%20has%20directed%20its%20partners%20working%20in%20India%20to%20halt%20projects.%20%26quot%3BThe%20recipient%20shall%20not%20resume%20work%20under%20this%20agreement%20until%20notification%20has%20been%20received%20in%20writing%20from%20the%20Agreement%20Officer%20(USAID)%20that%20this%20award%20suspension%20has%20been%20cancelled%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20directive%20states%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Times%20Of%20India%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSAID%20has%20been%20working%20in%20India%20for%20over%2070%20years.%20During%20the%20current%20fiscal%20year%2C%20India%20was%20to%20receive%20%24140%20million%20through%20USAID%20while%20the%20country's%20overall%20budget%20of%20over%20%24600%20billion%2C%20reported%20the%20news%20agency%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fiscal%202023-24%2C%20the%20USAID%20allocation%20was%20%246.8%20million%20for%20%26quot%3Bgovernment%20and%20civil%20society%26quot%3B%3B%20about%20%2455%20million%20for%20health%3B%20%2418%20million%20for%20environment%2C%20and%20%247.8%20million%20for%20%26quot%3Bsocial%20infrastructure%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%20government's%20Foreign%20Assistance%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20funding%20to%20India%20comes%20from%20USAID%2C%20health-related%20programmes%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20impacted%20most%2C%20followed%20by%20education%2C%20gender%20and%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealth%2C%20Education%2C%20WASH%2C%20And%20Food%20Security%3A%20USAID's%2070-Year%20Journey%20In%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealth%20Support%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSAID%20works%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20address%20various%20health%20challenges%20including%20maternal%20and%20child%20mortality%2C%20tuberculosis%20(TB)%2C%20HIV%20and%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%201990%2C%20USAID%20has%20helped%20save%20the%20lives%20of%20more%20than%202%20million%20children%20in%20India.%2025%2C000%20pneumonia%20deaths%20and%2014%2C000%20diarrhoea%20deaths%20were%20prevented%20through%20USAID%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20better%20diagnose%2C%20cure%2C%20and%20prevent%20TB%2C%20USAID%20supports%20the%20Indian%20government%20with%20its%20national-level%20campaign%2C%20the%20Call%20to%20Action%20for%20a%20TB-free%20India.%20In%20urban%20settings%2C%20USAID%20has%20trained%20health%20providers%20to%20expand%20access%20to%20TB%20services%20and%20improve%20the%20quality%20and%20adherence%20to%20international%20TB%20standards%20for%20diagnosis%2C%20treatment%2C%20and%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%201995%2C%20USAID%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20government%20and%20civil%20society%2C%20has%20worked%20to%20improve%20prevention%20and%20care%20for%20populations%20most%20at%20risk%20of%20HIV.%20With%20this%2C%20the%20number%20of%20new%20AIDS%20infections%20has%20reduced%20by%2032%20per%20cent%20since%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20USAID%20announced%20nearly%20%2413.1%20million%20in%20funding%2C%20to%20disseminate%20essential%20public%20health%20messages%20to%20communities%2C%20strengthen%20testing%20and%20surveillance%20and%20train%20Community%20Health%20Officers.%20USAID%20also%20donated%20200%20brand-new%2C%20state-of-the-art%20ventilators%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPartnership%20For%20Education%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSAID%20and%20its%20partners%20are%20working%20across%2016%20states%20to%20improve%20reading%20skills%20in%20nine%20languages.%20USAID%20supported%20India's%20literacy%20campaign%20Padhe%20Bharat%20Badhe%20Bharat%20(Read%20India%2C%20Progress%20India)%2C%20reaching%20more%20than%20two%20million%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSAID-supported%20programs%20trained%20over%2061%2C000%20teachers%20in%20improved%20teaching%20skills.%20They%20trained%20teachers%20to%20use%20flashcards%2C%20games%2C%20storytelling%2C%20and%20group%20work%20to%20motivate%20and%20engage%20their%20students%20more%20successfully.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWASH%20In%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSAID%20backed%20up%20the%20government's%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Abhiyan%20(Clean%20India%20Mission)%20launched%20in%202014%20and%20helped%20over%203%20lakh%20people%20with%20access%20to%20household%20toilets%2C%20ensuring%2025%2C000%20communities%20are%20open%20defecation%20free%20(ODF).%20It%20secured%20more%20than%20%245%20million%20in%20funding%20from%20the%20private%20sector%20to%20implement%20WASH%20solutions.%20Additionally%2C%2042%2C000%20toilets%20were%20located%20on%20Google%20Maps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFood%20Security%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%201.32%20lakh%20farmers%20have%20raised%20their%20yields%20and%20income%20by%20applying%20USAID-supported%20improved%20technologies%20and%20management%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSAID%20collaborated%20with%20India's%20largest%20weather%20services%20company%20to%20expand%20its%20network%20of%20automatic%20weather%20stations%20in%20nine%20states.%20It%20is%20to%20send%20reliable%2C%20localised%20weather%20data%2C%20risk%20mitigation%20tools%2C%20and%20crop%20insurance%20services%20by%20SMS%20to%20about%2070%2C000%20climate-vulnerable%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUSAID's%20Website%20Goes%20Offline%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20350%20US%20government%20websites%2C%20including%20that%20of%20USAID%2C%20have%20become%20unavailable.%20These%20included%20sites%20linked%20to%20the%20Departments%20of%20defense%2C%20commerce%2C%20energy%2C%20transportation%2C%20labor%2C%20the%20Central%20Intelligence%20Agency%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20whether%20the%20websites%20were%20temporarily%20offline%20or%20taken%20down%20at%20Trump's%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20above%20information%20has%20been%20sourced%20from%20the%20content%20archived.%20The%20information%20was%20released%20online%20before%20January%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPast%20And%20Present%20Of%20USAID%20Fund%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSAID%20is%20said%20to%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Blargest%20humanitarian%20and%20development%20arm%20of%20the%20US%20government%26quot%3B%2C%20with%20a%20workforce%20of%20approximately%2010%2C000%20people.%20In%20the%202023%20fiscal%20year%2C%20USAID%20managed%20more%20than%20%2440%20billion%20in%20funds%2C%20representing%20around%200.7%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20US%20government's%20%246.1%20trillion%20in%20spending%20during%20that%20period.%C2%A0The%20fund%20supported%20130%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20development%20assistance%20began%20after%20World%20War%202%20ended%20in%201945.%20George%20C%20Marshall%2C%20the%20Secretary%20of%20State%20from%201947%20to%201949%20provided%20significant%20financial%20and%20technical%20assistance%20to%20Europe%20after%20the%20war.%20Known%20as%20the%20Marshall%20Plan%2C%20it%20helped%20Europe%20to%20rebuild%20its%20infrastructure%2C%20strengthen%20its%20economy%2C%20and%20stabilise%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20the%20Marshall%20Plan%20prompted%20President%20Harry%20S%20Truman%20to%20propose%20an%20international%20development%20assistance%20program.%20In%201961%2C%20President%20Kennedy%20signed%20the%20Foreign%20Assistance%20Act%20into%20law%20and%20created%20USAID%20by%20executive%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Trump%20has%20taken%20charge%20of%20the%20US%20as%20the%2047th%20President%2C%20USAID%20and%20its%20operations%20have%20come%20under%20scrutiny.%20Musk%20has%20alleged%2C%20that%20USAID%20%26quot%3Bfunded%20bioweapon%20research%2C%20including%20Covid-19%2C%20that%20killed%20millions%20of%20people%26quot%3B%20using%20taxpayers'%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738644720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F4mpl2vbg_usaid-in-india_625x300_04_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-explainer-how-trumps-decision-to-shut-usaid-may-hit-projects-in-india-7629520%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20Donald%20Trump%20asked%20to%20realign%20foreign%20aid%2C%20USAID%20issued%20a%20directive%20asking%20all%20organisations%20implementing%20projects%20with%20its%20support%20in%20India%20to%20suspend%20work%20until%20further%20notice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-explainer-how-trumps-decision-to-shut-usaid-may-hit-projects-in-india-7629520%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20forces%20Pa