d%20his%20thoughts%20on%20the%20new%20income%20tax%20slabs.%20%26quot%3BOnly%20IT%20folks%20are%20crying%20about%20today's%20tax%20rebate%20up%20to%2012L.%20For%20many%20in%20non-IT%20fields%2C%2012L%20is%20a%20dream%20salary%20even%20after%207-10%20years%20of%20experience.%20These%20IT%20folks%20earning%2024L%2B%20should%20stop%20calling%20themselves%20%26quot%3Blower%20middle%20class.%26quot%3B%20Forget%2012L-check%20the%20median%20salary%20of%20India%20and%20see%20where%20you%20stand.%20Acting%20like%20you're%20poor%20with%20a%2024L%20salary%3F%20Please%20stop%20the%20nonsense%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20this%2C%20a%20fintech%20enthusiast%20claimed%20that%20anything%20less%20than%20Rs%2060%20lakh%20per%20annum%20is%20%26quot%3Bpoor%26quot%3B.%20The%20user%20explained%20that%2070%25%20of%20the%20income%20is%20paid%20as%20taxes%20like%20GS%20and%20VAT%20and%20anyone%20earning%20Rs%202%20lakh%20per%20month%20is%20middle%20class.%20%26quot%3BLess%20than%202LPM%20net-%20is%20middle%20class.%20People%20making%2060L-1cr%20are%20middle%20class.%20Those%20making%20above%201cr%2B%20are%20upper%20middle%20class.%20You%20aren't%20rich%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20generational%20wealth%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20user%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAnything%20less%20than%2060LPA%20is%20poor.%20You%20pay%2070%25%20income%20as%20taxes%20in%20the%20form%20of%20GST%2C%20income%20tax%20%26amp%3B%20VAT.%20Less%20than%202LPM%20net-%20is%20middle%20class.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnPeople%20making%2060L-1cr%20are%20middle%20class.%20Those%20making%20above%201cr%2B%20are%20upper%20middle%20class.%20You%20aren't%20rich%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20generational%20wealth.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FylwyUBWppr%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FylwyUBWppr%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Shark%20(%40fintech_shark)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%